quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  11,89,"“Uye imi vanhu vangu! Musave munoita kuti kupokana kwangu (kupikisana kwangu nemi panyaya dzekusatenda) kuve kunokonzera rushambwa urwo rwakafanana nerwakavinga vanhu vaNowa kana kuti vaHud kana kuti vaSwaalih rwukuvingeiwo (rwukurwadziseiwo), uye vanhu vaLoti havasi kure nemi zvakanyanya!”"
  11,90,"“Uye kumbirai ruregero kuna Tenzi venyu uye tendeukirai kwavari. Zvirokwazvo, Tenzi vangu ndivo vane tsitsi dzose, nerudo rwose.”"
  11,91,"Vakati: “Iwe Shuaib! Hatisi kunzwisisa pane zvizhinji zvaunotaura, uye tinokuona usina simba (zvinonzi aiva bofu) pakati pedu. Dai kusiri kuti mhuri yako, ingadai zvirokwazvo takakutema nematombo, uye hauna simba kupinda isu.”"
  11,92,"Iye akati: “Imi vanhu! Saka munoti mhuri yangu yakakosha kwamuri kupfuura Allah here? Uye munovakandira kumashure kwenyu. Zvirokwazvo, Tenzi vangu vanoziva (vanokomberedza) zvose zvamunoita.”"
  11,93,"“Uye imi vanhu vangu! Itai zvamunokwanisa nenzira yenyu, uye zvirokwazvo ndichaitawo (nenzira yangu). Muchaziva kuti kuna ani kuchasvikira marwadzo achamunyadzisa, uye ndiani munyepi! Uye Tarirai imi! Zvirokwazvo, neni ndakatarisawo nemi.”"
  11,94,"Asi pakauya murairo wedu, takanunura (takachengetedza) Shuaib uye neavo vaitenda pamwechete naye netsitsi dzedu. Uye marwadzo akasvikira vaiti vezvakaipa, uye vakarara (vakafa), vakapfugama mudzimba dzavo"
  11,95,Sekunge vasina kumbogaramo! Nokudaro ngaive kure Madyan (Midian) kufana nekure kweThamood! (Nzvimbo dzose idzi dzakaparadzwa)
  11,96,"Uye zvirokwazvo, takatumira Musa nezviratidzo zvedu nesimba riri pachena"
  11,97,"Kuna Farawo nemadzimambo ake, asi vakatevera murairo hwaFarawo, uye murairo hwaFarawo hwakanga usiri pagwara rechokwadi"